(3^n)\gt (n^4)
n=8
3^8>8^4
(1)
(2)
(2)
                   3^n>n^4,    (n\geq 8) ....(1) 
 3>\left(\frac{n+1}{n}\right)^4, (n\geq 8).....(2) 
 3^{n+1}>(n+1)^4. 
 \left(\frac{n+1}{n}\right)^4=\left({1+\frac{1}{n}}\right)^4=1+\frac{4}{n}+\frac{6}{n^2}+\frac{4}{n^3}+\frac{1}{n^4}. 
 \frac{4}{n}+\frac{6}{n^2}+\frac{4}{n^3}<1, (n\geq 6) 
 \left(\frac{n+1}{n}\right)^4<3, (n\geq 6) 
